        <hl1>Cheney's Energy Plan</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Richard Kassel (Natural Resources Defense Council) assails Vice Pres Dick Cheney's energy program (May 1 article)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
